Overview
This Spotify Clone is a web application(Frontend) designed to replicate some of the core functionalities of Spotify, including user registration, login, music browsing, and playlist creation. It is built using HTML, CSS.

Features
ğŸ†• User Registration: Allow new users to register for an account.
ğŸ” User Login: Authenticate existing users.
ğŸ” Search Music: Search for songs and artists.
ğŸ¶ Browse Music: Browse music by genres, albums, and artists.
ğŸ“‚ Create Playlist: Users can create and manage their playlists.
â–¶ï¸ Play Music: Play selected songs and control playback.
