ğŸŒ Web Server (e.g., Apache, Nginx)
Installation
Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/spotify-clone.git
cd spotify-clone
Run the Application
ğŸŒ Start the Web Server: Ensure your web server and MySQL server are running.
ğŸ–¥ï¸ Access the Application: Open your web browser and navigate to the application URL.
Folder Structure
ğŸ“ assets: Contains images, stylesheets, and other static assets.
ğŸ“ pages: Contains main pages like home, search, and playlists.
Usage
Register
Navigate to the registration page.
Fill in the required details.
Submit the form to create an account.
Login
Navigate to the login page.
Enter your credentials.
Submit the form to log in.
Search and Browse Music
Use the search bar to find your favorite songs or artists.
Browse music by genre, album, or artist from the home page.
Create and Manage Playlists
Navigate to the playlist section.
Create a new playlist or select an existing one.
Add or remove songs from your playlists.
Play Music
Select a song to play.
Use the playback controls to play, pause, or skip tracks.
